a) Do the same damage than a warrior<br>
b) Tank a bit worse than a warrior<br>
c) Have a bit less hp that a warrior<br>
d) Have spells to compensate for   b &amp; c<br>
<br>
Pal/SK traded some hp/tanking to get spells.<br>
<br>
If a warrior does 75dps on a mob, and takes 400dps MTing it.<br>
A paladin should do 75dps, and take 440 dps MTing it.<br>
<br>
The problem is if paladins/sk get the same hp/tanking as warriors.<br>
Warriors shall become totally useless (they tank the same &amp; dont agro at all).<br>
The the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>    i already have 600 less hp </i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
does dont compensate the uberness of spells for Tanking. You need to add something more.<br>
<br>
Warrior : 7000hp, 400dps : Lets say we use a 6 second rotation<br>
Paladin/SK : 6400hp 440dps : We will use a 5 second rotation<br>
<br>
You will trade some healing power (they are less efficient) for better agro control.<br>
<br>
A warrior will and must tank better, but with decent agro control.<br>
A Pal/SK will and must tank a bit worse, but with great agro control.<br>
<br>
I know about snare glands, i use them myself.<br>
But they are available to everyone, so id like to skip them.<br>
<br>
Why do u think everyone uses SK OOR for AL MTing ?<br>
Because its better agro management.<br>
<br>
So far i have nerver died due to a cleric running OOM<br>
(with the normal 3 magi + 1 shaman mod rod group).<br>
Mana on luclin is not a problem, so going for 6 to 5 or Sec rotation either.<br>
<br>
Warriors are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  great tanks</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> that <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  cant agro</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> naturally.<br>
Pal/SK are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  decent tanks</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> that <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  can agro</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> very well.<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>  VI must make Pal/Sk <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> GOOD</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> tanks and not <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Decent</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> as they are now.</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uemiliaeq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>EmiliaEQ</A> at: 8/20/02 11:44:12 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=711.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=711.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=711.topic&index=0><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=711.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.threadControl?topicID=711.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=711.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=711.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacin